Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.11,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個機關會吸收智世多餘的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到了早上就會綻開結晶的花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然看起來很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明跟我們很像 看起來卻很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.53,0:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 還有那些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}林德爾送了龍褪下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魚是西魯基送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}賽門送了手錶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡是送了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她做得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 借我一下你在蟻冢拿到的魔繩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會將製造吸收魔力的能力降到接近零
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很適合你的身體呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好了 不要擅自實驗和施放魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在幾乎什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明收下了許多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但無法做任何回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然身體還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我願意做任何去行動就能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 我去跟賽門先生道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也跟你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你又偷偷去倫敦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會再瞞著你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這很難說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真難得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都沒有人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是聖誕節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問你有看到過一個小男孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前有看過她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 她突然說弟弟不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們家就只有她一個孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求求你幫忙找我的弟弟 伊森吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫史黛拉‧巴克雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁聖誕假期來外婆家過節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟家人一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我帶伊森去了後園
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他身體明明很虛弱 但就是都不回屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之後我們吵了架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不想要你這種任性的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說了 伊森消失我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伊森是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有我一個記得弟弟 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然忘記自己的小孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你願意付出什麼代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}代價？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們在幫助人的時候 會收下對等的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你會為我們做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來這裡的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每個月最少會來這裡一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會做很多很多點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你抱都抱不完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想要錢的話 我會打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算花上一輩子也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是代價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是唷 他是魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是魔法使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很害怕吧 發生了這麼多怪事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然覺得可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.56,0:07:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這些事都沒有弟弟回不來可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.74,0:07:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}狗說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從這裡消失的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分散開會很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不要跟丟任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼 真美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿著這個就不怕走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會小心拿好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有人在妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}問問這附近的鄰居好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是不知道它們會不會說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你遇到麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夜之愛子是蜂后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蜂后能產卵 所以受其他蜂照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是魔法 所以沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以交涉方法來說還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請告訴我這孩子的弟弟在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事 你在和誰說話呀 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉不用在意 會有危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道 我想要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕 已經沒有花了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 讓她講詳細點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半茶杯的量 不許再多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你怎麼流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 你不用擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 我當然會擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你都做了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她在支付代價
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們不是魔法使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要搞到自己受傷 應該也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們並不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前也有一個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但已經再也見不到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想讓史黛拉能再見到你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在只能用這種方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很期待你的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回去要立刻包紮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 智世 讓你做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我自己說要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.65,0:11:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑到這麼遠的地方 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}灰眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個小孩被人拋棄在雪地裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還回來 他是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這話說得真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拋棄他的人 不就是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們會仔細聽人們說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}語言和文字是凝聚靈魂的聲與形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦傳達給別人 就再也不能收回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不想要你這種任性的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是真心那麼說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.49,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你根本不知道你的話會招致什麼後果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸好你沒有要他去死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和你弟弟的緣分已經斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在 他的前任姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能想起你弟弟的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 是叫{\bord0\blur10}伊森{\r\blur5}吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}緣分已斷就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}名字 年齡 出生地 長相 聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就連他的存在都會被忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他已經屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你支付得起這代價嗎 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要來玩一個遊戲 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也一起吧 影之子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們兩個人去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時限就到日落為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那之前能找到他們的話 就算你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輸了的話 他們就屬於我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這對我們不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你什麼也不會失去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你太自私妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你那野獸的鼻子 拼命地尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}冬天的白晝可是很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 我真的會把他忘記嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要找到就行了吧 找到就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遠東的你和西方的他都能夠相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這麼小的山丘上 怎麼可能見不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也是當姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要相信你和你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然想念到會失聲痛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們的緣分就沒那麼容易被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管是家人還是什麼 都一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 一起去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 你能聞得出氣味嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能被藏起來了 氣味非常淡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你那野獸的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲 你照顧下史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 用那個沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經認定自己的歸宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.06,0:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被困住了 幾乎動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種老東西力量太強大 真是頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是智世現在用魔法就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可真像你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你認識我姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是骷髏頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戴著頭骨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以取下來嗎 還是天生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會應付小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.45,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}變成人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能想起姐姐的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 不記得了 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說過吧 「我不要囉嗦的姐姐」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的不要了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真覺得家人不寶貴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這又不是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為那樣很丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是很懂家人或夫婦的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我有血親 是不是就能理解這種情感了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從來沒想過血緣關係的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算沒有血緣關係 家人就是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是長期一同生活 互相幫助的群體單位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣說的 好像什麼人都能當家人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也許 我現在超想和姐姐道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也想要一起參加派對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想和姐姐之外的人參加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為是家人 我才會這麼去想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跑起來 跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用鼻子 聞出氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}屬於我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你為什麼變成我的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小孩子的好奇心太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟我回家 聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不想要我這樣的弟弟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想我當你的姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望我的弟弟就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說了 我也就認識你這個弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也覺得 你當我姐姐就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}應該說「想要你當我姐姐」 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起名字了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好神奇 衣服居然沒有濕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法叫名字真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是場愉悅的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.15,0:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是相當愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能欣賞他人認真的樣子真是愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人的話語很有分量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因此我們會時常在人類身旁靜聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽著 一無所有的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被切斷的緣分 我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是有一樣東西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個東西似乎更美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還給你們好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被愚弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 你們跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她叫智世 是我今天交到的新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太謝謝你了 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我 你住哪裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會守約去你家的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉可是很固執的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說什麼啦
Comment: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:33.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:37.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:47.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:57.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}追いかけ合う　闇と光が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:10.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}二つの対なるもので
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創られてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:16.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この世の総べては
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:23.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あなたがいるから私はいる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:29.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}離れてもそばにいる（そばにいる）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:35.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}誰もが自分の　もう一つの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:42.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}片割れという　大切なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:50.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}探し続けてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:33.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}望著月亮 殘缺的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.13,0:22:37.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.98,0:22:47.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}選擇了遠路 並肩啟程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:57.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互相吸引的紅與黑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.62,0:23:04.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}相互追趕的光與暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:10.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}對立的兩種存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:12.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:16.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世間的芳華絢爛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:23.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只有你在 才有我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:29.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我們形影不離（形影不離）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:35.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}夢寐以求的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:42.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}屬於我們的另一半
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:50.06,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\1c&H05374D&\3vc(&H92DDEB&,&H92DDEB&,&HF1F1F1&,&HF1F1F1&)}我們卻仍在尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次交到朋友 少女內心歡欣雀躍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而 因為交到了這個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少女和魔法使之間的關係 產生了一點扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在哪裡 智世
